34:34.441 --> 34:37.384
picture made while I'm sitting. That's 
beautiful, yeah. If you well can see, sitting in

34:38.665 --> 34:41.288
his lap. We'll have to use that picture, too. 
That's a nice photograph of all of you. But they

34:46.373 --> 34:49.717
couldn't understand why. I said, if you'll just 
look back at all the pictures, I'm just always as

34:50.097 --> 34:57.205
close to him as I can be. And that one, sitting in his 
lap. Yeah, for sure. Yeah. So that was the family.

35:06.367 --> 35:15.659
The picture hanging in the boyhood home of us in 
1916, I'm holding Lennon's little sister. Which

35:16.280 --> 35:17.281
one that was? That was Lucia. Lucia. She was born in 
1916. I'm holding her. So what year were you born?

35:25.352 --> 35:25.832
What day? What hour? Well, the day and hour... I was 
born in 1905 at 6

35:31.816 --> 35:45.201
o'clock in the afternoon, the hottest day my 
